window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Newbery Medal Winner, 1985</b></p> <p>Uncertain of the past, Aerin-sol, daughter of King Arlbeth, decides to forge her own future by challenging the lashing tongues of the dragon’s fire. Aerin’s proficiency as \"the Dragon-slayer\" sets her on a quest for the stolen Crown of Damar, believed to be in the hands of rebellious northerners who threaten to destroy the Damarian people and their home forever.</p>"; 
